These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, van
2 different pets are kept: goat, turtle
1. the owner of the goat is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the turtle is the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Transport   | van | boat |
| Pet     | turtle    | goat   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
House: victorian, farmhouse
2 different pets are kept: turtle, snake
1. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4
2. the farmhouse house is on the left of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| House   | farmhouse | victorian        |
| Pet      | turtle  | snake |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
There 2 different types of food: artichoke, radish
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, montecristo
1. the swisher-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating radish is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Food   | radish    | artichoke |
| Cigar   | swisher | montecristo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, bike
2 different games are played: domino, billiard
1. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person playing billiard is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Transport   | helicopter      | bike |
| Game       | domino | billiard    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
