 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, cola
There 2 different types of food: carrot, potato
1. the person eating carrot is in an even position##4
2. the person eating potato is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Beverage       | cola | soy-milk  |
| Food   | potato  | carrot |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-7::.
