 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-8::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: comedy, romance
City: prague, san-francisco
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | romance |
| City           | san-francisco       | prague       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-9::.
