The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, november
1. the person who's birthday is in february is in an even position##4
2. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |
| Food           | tomato | carrot |
| Birthday   | november | february    |

